" cndent rule: Indent java anonymous classes correctly.
":set cinoptions=j1

" Reserving these variables don't make a lot of sense for NodeJS:
" (e.g. top, window, ...)
syntax clear javaScriptMember
syntax clear javaScriptGlobal

